data.title: Former LSU Tiger Linked to Superstar Kim Kardashian
data.meta_description: Is the relationship between Kim Kardashian and Odell Beckham Jr. a real thing?
data.text:
SHREVEPORT, LA – Former LSU Tiger and current Baltimore Ravens star wide receiver Odell Beckham Jr. is reportedly in a relationship with one of the worlds most talked about celebrity.

People magazine says Beckham Jr. has been hanging out with Kim Kardashian, but the report says it’s casual right now. The 43-year-old reality star and business mogul has been dating the 31-year-old football star for about five months, though they have been keeping things pretty low key.

An insider tells People:

“Neither of them are in any big hurry to jump into something serious.”

We got a little look inside this relationship when The Kardashians star showed up at Beckham’s 31st birthday bash in New York City.

Who Was Beckham Linked to Before Kardashian?

Beckham recently broke up with his model girlfriend, Lauren Wood. The couple has a son together who is now 2-years-old.

Kardashian has been linked to other athletes, including New Orleans Saints star Reggie Bush back in 2007. They broke up about 3 years later.

She was married to Kanye West for about 7 years and they have four children together.

Odell Beckham Jr.'s Football Career

Beckham played for LSU from 2011-2013. He played at Isidore Newman High School in New Orleans.

He was drafted by the New York Giants, but he has also played for Cleveland, Los Angeles and now Baltimore.
